{
  "stem": "20848.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there were again Polish women notice what happened, and they quickly put my number down to go to the transport. 2,000 women they picked up that day.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they-- we marched.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they marched us to a man camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I don't know why they march us to a man camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But we were sitting there on the floor in the-- in the men's camp when all of a sudden there came an order for us to get up, and they were-- we marching.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And behind us was going ambulance, a Red Cross ambulance.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was thinking to myself, isn't it nice of them to have an ambulances in case somebody gets sick or something?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they marched us to gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Only I didn't know at the time it was gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, a few years ago, I met a lady who was in my transport and we talked about it. 2,000 of us.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they put us in gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I-- I remember it looked to me like a sauna, because they were, you know, the showers coming from the ceiling.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was no windows.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was a door.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And a little window like you see above, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Very narrow little window.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my mother and I sat near the door.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we sat there and sat there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we sat there the whole night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We thought that any minute-- we're so stupid that we still didn't know where we were.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Of course, we heard about gassing, but we didn't know that the gas is coming through the shower like it-- made to look like shower so people wouldn't panic, you know?",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's where the gas was coming through.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
